you should use podman instead of docker:
https://k3d.io/v5.4.0/usage/advanced/podman/

pacman -S argocd kubectl fuse-overlayfs podman helm argocd glab
paru -S k3d

demolinux specific:
install `fuse-overlayfs` but do not modify /etc/containers/storage.conf
ensure /var/lib/containers is a symlink to /data/containers
